{"tid":986562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★富士康鄭州iphone廠房已裁員5萬人！裝配工人被要求在年底前離職","createTime":"2019-01-18T14:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T15:30:00.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4cbc8af4f052a23079b12be38a5d8d446d2a1829","tid":986562,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T14:37:08.000Z","msg":"日媒報道，富士康鄭州廠房自去年10月至今，已解僱約5萬名合約員工。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述消息人士指，富士康正常會在iPhone生產淡季期間縮減合約員工，往年會從8月起到1月底期間，以每月續約的方式與員工簽約，是次削減員工的規模，未必較前一年大，只是時間有所提早。<br />\n<br />\n不過，據知情人士指，裝配工人被要求在年底前離職，情況與去年有別。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190118/bkn-20190118212844723-0118_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190118%2Fbkn-20190118212844723-0118_00842_001.html&d=asQxQC2wHI%2FrIUCZzsO9mDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5d25c6ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190118/bkn-20190118212844723-0118_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"55ff2cae4e002094866857b55e7549ac20c0e595","tid":986562,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T14:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902dab57f8257b84d372f1450a41f962332d855b","tid":986562,"uid":100131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T14:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29986e06b7792ba04288c0660d91cf03a8d4ff99","tid":986562,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T14:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\"